An easy-to-learn online plateforme.

   e-mail signatures

Strengthen your image.

   Boost My Mail automates the management of all your corporate email
   signatures. In order to design a uniform signature, you just have to
   chose one template. Boost My Mail will then integrate and synchronize
   the e-mail adresses of your staff in real time in order to connect them
   to the template. Very easy!
   Request a demo
   Personnaliser Signature Mail Déploiement Outlook Gmail Mail Max Office
   365 Exchange
   Bannière Mail Campagne de communication A/B testing Statistiques

   E-mail Banners

Deploy your communication campaigns.

   Thanks to Boost My Mail, you can add banners to the staff’s e-mail
   signatures. It will help you promote your organisation’s events or
   special offers. It is an opportunity to target a special audience in a
   non-intrusive way. Use every outgoing e-mail to communicate!
   More information

   Tracking

Measure the return on investment.

   With Boost My Mail you can measure the efficiency of your email
   signatures and communication campaigns. You can check the amount of
   clicks generated on the links you inserted in the signatures. It is an
   indispensable tool to personalize your offers!
